another query that's slow is this: [https://cloud.mongodb.com/v2/66d97e86f0a8301d0706bb04#/metrics/replicaSet/66d981f4590ef12099612c1e/queryInsights/profiler/details/meraki_prod.cartmodels/query](https://cloud.mongodb.com/v2/66d97e86f0a8301d0706bb04#/metrics/replicaSet/66d981f4590ef12099612c1e/queryInsights/profiler/details/meraki_prod.cartmodels/query) 

The issue is that it's not using pushed_to_kafka index, which would be much more efficient, since there would only be few documents with it false. If we can add a mongodb index hint, to use that index, this query will become much faster as well.

